    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Choose your Wizard!</h2>Master of the Wizards is a party card game for 4 to 6 players in which you control a respectable wizard. On this demo, you can play as Fumbledolphus, the Scholar, against 5 other AI wizards!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/d3a0067621e89be06f48190b543760f0.avif?t=1632538134\" width=616 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Conquer strange lands!</h2><br>Conquer Lands to gain influence throughout the realms and some extra power. Reach 20 points of influence to win the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/Description---Conquer-Strange-Lands.png?t=1632538134\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cast powerful spells!</h2><br>Target other Wizards with your mighty Attack Spells. Be the last Wizard standing to win the game. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/Description---Cast-Powerful-Spells.png?t=1632538134\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buff yourself!</h2><br>Increase your power with Buff Spells to get the upper hand.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/6e539395fe9ddff0aedab545a7248d7a.avif?t=1632538134\" width=616 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Curse your rivals!</h2><br>Cast Curse Spells upon rival Wizards to make their life miserable.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/26f3b5e5f5b93e105d7e56edc5844fa1.avif?t=1632538134\" width=616 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And Chain their spells right back at them!</h2><br>Answer your enemies' attacks with Chain Spells to make them someone else's problem... But beware of being a Chain target yourself!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/7f070ae6c587f77c6e6d4dd04f93c909.avif?t=1632538134\" width=616 height=220 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenge your friends!</h2><br>Battle for the title of...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746740/extras/7242ca868da3b06788e8904e5b6943df.avif?t=1632538134\" width=616 height=220 /></span>",
